erable\ndecrease in computational time for the presented iterative approach applied to\nvarious compact and chain-type molecules, while supporting sufficient accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Feb 2016 16:51:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
