cal distribution of 56Ni suggested here. According to its optical\nproperties, SN2014J looks as a normal SNIa. So it is extremely important to\ndiscern if it is also representative in the gamma-ray band.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2016 10:01:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
